Motormaster can see Megatron soaring towards him in the distance, he grabs
his Cyclone gun from the ground, and immidiately starts firing on Megatron.

Down on the shore, the other Decepticons look on in awe (just mine guys).
Sinnertwin arrives back at base, and lands beside Cyclonus, he then sees
the fight, "Fight? Sinnertwin want to fight" he says, getting ready to
leave again.

Megatron dodges skillfully around the blasts of Atom smashing energy that
are hurled at him, but there are to many, as one clips the right side of
his abdomen, and after exploding, leaves a clean cut, where the metal armor
was. Megatron lifts his arms up, and his back cannon loads underneath them,
and fires a burst at Motormaster, that hits its target, sending him
sprawling to the ground. Megatron lands, and attempts to kick his opponent.
